dc_title_s: Delaware River Channel Showing Existing Depths
dc_description_s: Map shows existing depths of various ranges of the Delaware River, as well as the date in which they were sounded. The ranges include: Lower Horseshoe, Upper Horseshoe, Mifflin, Billingsport Connecting, Tincum, Schooner Ledge, Bellevue, Cherry Island, Deep Water Point, New Castle, Reedy Island, Liston, and Baker.
